    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>By now you have no doubt heard that the latest version of Drupal is due in early 2014. You may also be aware that it is shaping up to be a rather controversial release, even provoking a split in the community with a high profile fork of Drupal called Backdrop.</p>
<p>There are two things that have recently caught my attention and given me some concern regarding Drupal 8. First, having read various discussion threads and social media exchanges, I’m struck by the level of confusion and misinformation I’ve seen. There’s a lot of worry over Drupal 8 from people that actually stand to benefit greatly from it.</p>
<!--break-->
